Ask HN: How do recruiters deal with tons of applicants from public job boards?
text:
I'd estimate that there would be no less than 1000 applications from a single job post from public job listings.

How do recruiters sort out those applications? What is the initial criteria to filter out the low quality applications?

title: Show HN: Malibu for VSCode retro theme inspired by surfing days in Malibu Beach
text:
Installation
Open Extensions sidebar panel in VS Code. View → Extensions
Search for Malibu
Click Install to install it.
Code > Preferences > Color Theme > Malibu Sunset - Malibu Sunrise
